        <actionDate>2019-07-25</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2019-12-03T13:26:15Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p> This bill modifies the eligibility criteria for an elderly offender to qualify for early release from prison and placement in home detention. </p> <p>Specifically, it reduces the amount of a prison term an elderly offender must serve by the amount of good time credits earned by the offender. </p>]]></text>
